These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
Hobby: card-games, fishing, magic-tricks, filmmaking
1. Hobby:fishing is between Hobby:magic-tricks and Hobby:filmmaking##2
2. Hobby:fishing is on the left of Hobby:magic-tricks##1
3. Hobby:card-games is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Hobby   | card-games | filmmaking | fishing | magic-tricks |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
Sport: baseball, snowboarding, rugby, surfing
1. Sport:surfing is on the right of Sport:snowboarding##1
2. Sport:rugby is on the right of Sport:baseball##1
3. Sport:surfing is between Sport:snowboarding and Sport:baseball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Sport   | snowboarding | surfing | baseball | rugby |

 #################################
 
